      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BONDITRAM (8) broke his maiden status at Pinjarra last start when winning by 1.5L in good style. Tsang follows him out to Narrogin now and while this is a big jump in grade, he is a progressive type on the rise. Looks to shape nicely for him and he can bring up back-to-back wins. TOO MUCH TALK (2) hasn't been far away in recent events at the midweeks and rates highly coming back to a race at country level. Azzopardi knows the gelding well and reunites having guided him to 2 of his three career wins. Can put his best foot forward. IMAPAGETHREE GIRL (6) was too good as the race favourite here last start when sitting handy and getting over the top to win by 0.8L. Should get plenty of favours again this time around and can repeat the dose without surprising. CRUISE TO VICTORY (1) can feature first-up with an inside barrier. SPEED BUBBLE (5) likes this track and trip and can play a leading role on resumption with Nottle on board.",
